otdLevelDescription: Try these BEGINNER level quickies if you are new to exercising or need to ease back into it.
Perform these INTERMEDIATE quickies with solid technique before moving on to higher levels.
Some of these ADVANCED quickies may be harder than they appear.
These quickies are definitely challenging and are considered EXPERT level.
Attempt these quickies if you are a MASTER of calisthenics and enjoy an extremely tough challenge.
